text: Tedamali, also known as Telamali, is a Wayana village on the Lawa River in French Guiana. == Geography == Tedamali lies about upstream the Lawa river from Maripasoula. == Notable people == *Wayana Boy, a musician whose real name is David Khana, lives in Tedamali. == Notes == == References == * * Category:Villages in French Guiana
title: Tedamali
